{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 221.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Myself, I had many friends in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many friend, many schoolmates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are many those-- of my friends-- have left the ghetto in earlier times, and they went to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- Mostly, the fact that I was working in [NON-ENGLISH], I was able to-- I had a very good communication with the outside.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because across the street of [NON-ENGLISH], which is the factory marmalade, was the [NON-ENGLISH], which was a-- a place of the largest milk product place, where they used to make butter and cheese, and so far and so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I used to-- I found a way through underground from [NON-ENGLISH], where the pipes, the sewer pipes were, and some other type of pipes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to climb through these pipes and reach the other side of the street, and come in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I used to have a-- I befriended a Lithuanian, who used to give me butter and some other things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I used to bring them to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A few times they caught me, and they would beat me up, but it was not terrible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And once, the head of this [NON-ENGLISH] company was a German, a civilian, but he was very, very close to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he caught me taking some marmalade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he pointed out to me that next time, if he catches me, he's just going to take me to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that would mean the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But to, you know, forced to survive, you did anything you were able to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sometimes, I used to-- I was blondish when I was younger.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
